FBIS4-29906 "dreas120_c_94020" FBIS-EAS-94-120 Daily Report 19 Jun 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song Meets Wife of Former Japanese Leader Kim Il-song Meets Wife of Former Japanese Leader SK1906105894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1046 GMT 19 Jun 94 SK1906105894 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 19 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song today received Mutsuko Miki, the wife of a former Japanese prime minister, and her family on a visit to Korea. Present on the occasion was Chon Yon-ok, vice-chairwoman of the Korean Society for Cultural Relations with Foreign Countries. President Kim Il-song had a cordial and friendly talk with the guests. The guests presented a gift to him. President Kim Il-song gave a luncheon for the guests.
